description: Pelican Poboys is serving up some of the best New Orleans inspired cuisine on the West Coast! A healthier take on the classic sandwich, Pelican Poboys does not compromise on flavor when it brings you classic Cajun cuisine with their very own style. Along with their Red Beans & Rice and delicious Jambalaya, this food truck is ready to satisfy your Southern style cravings!
name: Pelican Poboys
